import {
  Box,
  Flex,
  Link,
  List,
  ListItem,
  Text,
  VStack,
  Icon,
  Image,
} from "@chakra-ui/react";
import {
  FaTwitter,
  FaGithub,
  FaInstagram,
  FaFacebook,
  FaLinkedin,
  FaYoutube,
  FaPinterest,
  FaReddit,
  FaDiscord,
  FaTwitch,
  FaVk,
} from "react-icons/fa";

const Footer = () => {
  return (
    <Box as="footer" py={12} bg="gray.50" color="gray.600" fontSize="sm">
      <Flex
        direction={{ base: "column", md: "row" }}
        justify="space-between"
        align="center"
        maxW="1200px"
        mx="auto"
        px={4}
      >
        <VStack align="flex-start" spacing={4}>
          <Image src="/logo.png" alt="My Graphics" w={40} h={40} />
          <Text>© 2023 My Graphics. All rights reserved.</Text>
        </VStack>
        <VStack align="flex-start" spacing={4}>
          <Text>Stay connected with me:</Text>
          <Flex align="center">
            <Link href="https://twitter.com/mygraphics" isExternal>
              <Icon as={FaTwitter} boxSize={6} mr={4} color="#1DA1F2" />
            </Link>
            <Link href="https://github.com/mygraphics" isExternal>
              <Icon as={FaGithub} boxSize={6} mr={4} color="#333" />
            </Link>
            <Link href="https://instagram.com/mygraphics" isExternal>
              <Icon as={FaInstagram} boxSize={6} mr={4} color="#E1306C" />
            </Link>
            <Link href="https://facebook.com/mygraphics" isExternal>
              <Icon as={FaFacebook} boxSize={6} mr={4} color="#4267B2" />
            </Link>
            <Link href="https://linkedin.com/in/mygraphics" isExternal>
              <Icon as={FaLinkedin} boxSize={6} mr={4} color="#2867B2" />
            </Link>
            <Link href="https://youtube.com/mygraphics" isExternal>
              <Icon as={FaYoutube} boxSize={6} mr={4} color="#FF0000" />
            </Link>
            <Link href="https://pinterest.com/mygraphics" isExternal>
              <Icon as={FaPinterest} boxSize={6} mr={4} color="#E60023" />
            </Link>
            <Link href="https://reddit.com/r/mygraphics" isExternal>
              <Icon as={FaReddit} boxSize={6} mr={4} color="#FF4500" />
            </Link>
            <Link href="https://discord.com/invite/mygraphics" isExternal>
              <Icon as={FaDiscord} boxSize={6} mr={4} color="#7289DA" />
            </Link>
            <Link href="https://twitch.tv/mygraphics" isExternal>
              <Icon as={FaTwitch} boxSize={6} mr={4} color="#6441A5" />
            </Link>
            <Link href="https://vk.com/mygraphics" isExternal>
              <Icon as={FaVk} boxSize={6} mr={4} color="#45668E" />
            </Link>
          </Flex>
        </VStack>
      </Flex>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Footer;
